  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>, java.util.RandomAccess, IPerambulateListActions<T>

    public class MS_List<T>
extends java.util.ArrayList<T>
implements IPerambulateListActions<T>
    Purpose of this class is to make lists of different objects. It's possible to perambulate list using methods from interface IPerambulateListActions.
    Version:
    1.1.
    See Also:
    IPerambulateListActions, Serialized Form
